From the last few days I have constantly been receiving some replies
like, "You only share the success stories, but don't tell anything
about losses"

You know Anand, when I started, even I didn't succeed at a
single attempt!

It took me a lot of backlashes, lot of pressure, lot of debts and a lot
of courage to reach this level...

You might be aware with some of them already which I had shared publicly
but there are still some stories that is just between me and my heart...

Success comes with a price, not in monetary terms, but far more than
that!

It tests your patience, your strength, your weaknesses, your endurance,
and overall YOU...

And after it's convinced that you are the right person to achieve
success, then only it comes to you...

The ones who give up, complain, and are dissatisfied are the ones who
will never taste success in life!

And the reason for me to share the success stories is not to do
promotion, but to motivate you to do better...¬†

The Traders whose profits you are seeing now are the ones who had
already made so much of losses but still rose up and bounced back
stronger...

**I am only the mediator, it's you who has to work hard, and it's you
who will be paid for the hardwork!**

**It's all YOU!**

I just wanted to say this...

And I will be happier if even 1 person gets motivated by me and improves
his/her life!

Regards,

**Ruchir Gupta**
